Description: The first multi-party elections since 1968, and only the second multi-party elections since independence in 1964.
After recently holding a one-party election, they lifted their ban on other political parties in 1992.
After over 100 years of German and South African control, they gained independence in 1990.
They were in the midst of a civil war that lasted from 1990-1995.
